    "note": "yir'ah invariant-bundle declarations (ADR-2606112200 D4) — adopted only where meaningful for this actor's scope; each declaration is grounded in the cited existing gates.",
    "declared": {
      "non-adjudicating": "files + tracks disclosure requests only — no characterization, no legal advice (G5); outcomes are recorded, never judged",
      "no-score-of-soul": "neither data subjects nor responding institutions are scored; response conduct is attested as fact, never rated",
      "map-not-target": "OWN data only — never a third party's PII, never a non-consenting person (G3); structurally the inverse of a target list",
      "append-only": "kotoba attestation lineage on every request/response (G2); nothing erased",
      "never-a-throne": "true requester always identified, no pretext (G4); disclosed PII only in encrypted envelopes (G6) — no central PII store"
